  "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nIn our application we want to connect to elastic search using oidc client but as I see only support for basic auth has been provided. I wanted to know if there is any other way to connect to elastic search using oidc client.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nConnects to Elastic search using oidc client\n\n### Actual behavior\n\nOnly basic auth is supported\n\n### How to Reproduce?\n\nhttps://quarkus.io/guides/elasticsearch\n\n### Output of `uname -a` or `ver`\n\nw\n\n### Output of `java -version`\n\n17.0.2\n\n### GraalVM version (if different from Java)\n\n17.0.2\n\n### Quarkus version or git rev\n\n2.8.2\n\n### Build tool (ie. output of `mvnw --version` or `gradlew --version`)\n\nmvnw\n\n### Additional information\n\nhttps://quarkus.io/guides/elasticsearch",
